@node history "History"
History :
~~~~~~~~~
 v0.5 : No big deal ; it was just an ordinary 'reset'-command.
 v0.7 : ReqTools-interface written.
 v0.9 : STAT-RAM support included.

 v1.0 : [FIRST PUBLIC RELEASE] - Should work fine now.

 v1.1 : ReqTools look changed.
        1.x no longer supported, sorry ...
 
 v1.2 : QUIET - option added.
        Code is now much smaller.

 v1.3 : Variable delay possible. DELAY - option added.
        Code extremely small now.

 v1.4 : Dropped StatRAM support. Sorry folks.

@endnode
                   
